title: Haase Unlimited My 1st Easter - First Bunny Egg Hunt Bodysuit
features: Are you searching for the perfect bodysuit to celebrate Easter? Look no further! This festive My 1st Easter - First Bunny Egg Hunt Bodysuit is a comfortable, very affordable way for your child to express themselves. Whether you are purchasing for a son, daughter, niece, nephew, or grandchild you can be sure to put a smile on their face.

Our designs are printed on a soft, comfortable, 100% combed ringspun cotton bodysuit. This amazing bodysuit will definitely become a staple in your child's wardrobe. Features a 1x1 baby rib and lap shoulders to make it easier for the numerous times a day parents must change the baby's outfit.

*SIZING & COLOR* : Please refer to size chart provided (*last image*) before buying for correct sizing specifications. If you are between sizes, or if you are looking for a looser fit, please order the next size up. Also please note that based on different computer displays, apparel colors may vary slightly from the image. Available in sizes Newborn-24 Months

*GARMENT CARE* : Fully Machine washable - Wash inside out in cold water, tumble dry on low heat. We recommend hang drying the garment. Do not iron directly on or on the backside of the graphic itself to ensure a long lasting print.

*EXCLUSIVE HAASE UNLIMITED DESIGN* : Professionally designed and printed exclusively by Haase Unlimited in the United States. Looking for other graphic shirts or a different garment? We carry apparel for the entire family! Click our brand name above, or search "Haase Unlimited" to find our full product line on amazon, including our best selling items!
